column4: GitLab gains developers after Microsoft buys rival GitHub
column5: Microsoft Corp's  decision to buy GitHub has been a blessing for rival U.S. coding platform GitLab  which has seen thousands of developers jump ship on worries that GitHub may end up favoring Microsoft products over others.

column4: Tesla shareholders defeat proposal to separate Musk's roles
column5: June 5 Tesla shareholders at an annual meeting on Tuesday re-elected three directors and voted against a proposal to split the chairman and chief executive jobs  both of which billionaire Elon Musk holds.
